{"tid":1486281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提提吹奏「只有和理非」才是正確道路的你","createTime":"2019-08-18T23:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:15:02.000Z","uid":4249,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"179042385270d1c79304aa62f6657da1ccb62ddd","tid":1486281,"uid":4249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔好自欺欺人，現實係<span style=\"color: green;\">和理非</span>又好<span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武</span>又好，2種路線都<span style=\"color: red;\">未曾成功</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武</span>出黎嘅日子，垃圾政府會「予以譴責」，<span style=\"color: green;\">和理非</span>出黎嘅活動，垃圾政府新聞稿都係寫句「大致和平」，跟手都係無理過你地。 所以唔好傻左咁以為2條路線有得到唔同嘅效果，以為自己可以判斷邊條路線距離成功近左。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">現實話俾大家聽，根本政府對任何方式抗爭都係無反應，所以我地唔需要為唔同嘅方法去評分，你想用邊種方法就請去做，同時唔好阻止其他人用唔同嘅方法表達訴求，因為大家都只係希望將諗到嘅方法試到會成功為止。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後，想提大家，邊種方式都好，五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8E1AQTT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8E1AQTT.png&h=20407888&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc3a5977b28370b32b0fd3d4443c79476a523fe6","tid":1486281,"uid":4249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:15:33.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯左係手機台，推呢個pls"},{"pid":"1997f9ac82b7191941bbcaf00b8a1ec579221bdd","tid":1486281,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:16:17.000Z","msg":"fair comment"},{"pid":"c13d756ff80099621c6d28c5df1171a17a982664","tid":1486281,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:17:06.000Z","msg":"和理勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695370c45bbb76e72697742054191cd834abd3ac","tid":1486281,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:17:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話2條腿走路<img src=\